Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.82,0:02:14.86,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}You think we're different
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.86,0:02:17.74,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}You think we never feel the way you do
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.74,0:02:20.24,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}We've got scars to prove we're too
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.24,0:02:22.12,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}Nothing but human
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.12,0:02:24.79,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}Fueled by emotions that we thought we knew
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.79,0:02:27.29,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}But really had no clue
